---
// Artista Karli - Geométrico con efectos de formas
---

<section id="artist-karli" class="artist-section relative min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/20 via-black to-purple-900/20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Geometric shapes background -->
  <div class="geometric-bg absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
    <div class="geometric-shape geometric-triangle"></div>
    <div class="geometric-shape geometric-circle"></div>
    <div class="geometric-shape geometric-square"></div>
    <div class="geometric-shape geometric-hexagon"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Artist Horizontal Content Wrapper -->
  <div class="artist-content-wrapper flex" style="width: 400vw;">
    
    <!-- Panel 1: Introducción -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl">
        <div class="artist-avatar mb-8">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b612b950?w=300&h=300&fit=crop&crop=face" 
            alt="Karli" 
            class="w-40 h-40 mx-auto rounded-full object-cover border-4 border-purple-500 shadow-2xl"
          />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-rye font-bold text-white mb-6">KARLI</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-purple-300 mb-4">Arquitecta de Líneas Geométricas</p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Donde la precisión matemática se encuentra con el arte. Cada diseño es una exploración 
          de formas, patrones y simetrías que transforman la piel en un lienzo geométrico.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 2: Portfolio Principal -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl">
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-triangle"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565058379802-bbe93b2986a5?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 1" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-circle"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611605698323-b1e99cfd37ea?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 2" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-square"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590246814883-57c511f96c5d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 3" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-hexagon"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1598300042247-d088f8ab3a91?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 4" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-triangle"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565058379802-bbe93b2986a5?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 5" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group geometric-container">
          <div class="geometric-shape small-circle"></div>
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590246814883-57c511f96c5d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Geométrico 6" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 3: Filosofía Geométrica -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-6xl items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-4xl font-rye font-bold text-purple-400 mb-6">Geometría Sagrada</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="geometry-element">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Precisión Matemática</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Cada línea se calcula con precisión milimétrica para lograr simetrías perfectas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="geometry-element">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Patrones Fractales</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Diseños que se repiten y evolucionan, creando composiciones hipnóticas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="geometry-element">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Simetría Perfecta</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300">Balance y armonía visual que trasciende lo decorativo para ser arte puro.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="artwork group">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611605698323-b1e99cfd37ea?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" 
            alt="Proceso de Karli" 
            class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-2xl group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Panel 4: Contacto & Especialidades -->
    <div class="artist-panel w-screen min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl">
        <h3 class="text-5xl font-rye font-bold text-purple-400 mb-8">Precisión en Cada Trazo</h3>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Si buscas un diseño que combine arte y matemáticas, donde cada línea tiene un propósito 
          y cada forma cuenta una historia geométrica.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Disponibilidad</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">Miércoles a Domingo: 12:00 - 20:00</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">Lunes y Martes: Diseño</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">Citas por agendamiento</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-info">
            <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Especialidades</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">• Mandalas</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-2">• Geometría Sagrada</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300">• Patrones Fractales</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-8 py-4 text-xl font-bold rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg">
          Agendar con Karli
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 right-8 text-white/70 z-30">
    <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Desliza →</span>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .artist-section {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .artist-content-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  
  .artist-panel {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .geometric-container {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  /* Formas geométricas de fondo */
  .geometric-shape {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0.3;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  
  .geometric-triangle {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #a855f7, #7c3aed);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 0% 100%, 100% 100%);
    top: 10%;
    left: 10%;
    animation: float 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .geometric-circle {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7);
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: 20%;
    right: 15%;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }
  
  .geometric-square {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(225deg, #a855f7, #7c3aed);
    bottom: 30%;
    left: 20%;
    animation: float 10s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  .geometric-hexagon {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(315deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7);
    clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);
    bottom: 15%;
    right: 25%;
    animation: float 7s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }
  
  /* Formas pequeñas para el portfolio */
  .small-triangle, .small-circle, .small-square, .small-hexagon {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: -10px;
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    opacity: 0.6;
    z-index: 10;
  }
  
  .small-triangle {
    background: #a855f7;
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 0% 100%, 100% 100%);
  }
  
  .small-circle {
    background: #7c3aed;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  
  .small-square {
    background: #a855f7;
  }
  
  .small-hexagon {
    background: #7c3aed;
    clip-path: polygon(25% 0%, 75% 0%, 100% 50%, 75% 100%, 25% 100%, 0% 50%);
  }
  
  .geometry-element {
    padding-left: 20px;
    border-left: 2px solid #a855f7;
  }
  
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg); }
  }
</style>
